name: De Omnibus Dubitandum
description:
My first NFT audio. 
Back in the day, i made so many ambience/drone tracks (circa 2003-2005) as a moniker ' Mesin Mesias' on MySpace. This is one from many tracks that saved by my friends ( thank God! )just before the site is collapsing. I'm not knewing it until now. Gonna mint all tracks one by one here.

De Omnibus Dubitandum is a tribute to Rene Descrates quotation " Everything must be doubted." I made this when entering adolescence filled with many questions in life.

'De Omnibus Dubitandum'
Audio by Mesin Mesias
Illustration by Space Wombats
